headline: Is the A320 Milestone a Sign of Further Gains for Airbus in 2025?
summary: If you have been following Airbus lately, you know it is not just another stalwart in the aerospace industry. It is a company steadily grabbing headlines and breaking records. Investors eyeing Airbus stock have enjoyed a handsome ride. The share price recently closed at 203.3, notching up gains of 0.4% over the last week, 5.2% for the month, and a remarkable 27.0% year-to-date. Stretching back even further, the stock has soared 53.1% in the past year and a stunning 225.0% over five years...

headline: Boeing Awarded Approximately $2.7 Billion in Multiyear Contracts for PAC‑3 Seeker Production
summary: Boeing [NYSE: BA] has been awarded a combination of multiyear contracts valued at approximately $2.7 billion to produce additional Patriot Advanced Capability‑3 (PAC‑3) seekers. Under the agreements, Boeing will deliver more than 3,000 seekers at rates of up to 750 units per year through 2030.
